Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.03,0:00:11.10,ASS,,0,0,0,,{\pos(954,882)}{\fad(800,800)}下午三点的人妻
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.85,0:00:20.91,ASS,,0,0,0,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.52,0:00:29.32,ASS,,0,0,0,,你好\N来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.32,0:00:31.31,ASS,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.59,0:00:34.99,ASS,,0,0,0,,要交给下一家唷
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.66,0:00:40.19,ASS,,0,0,0,,现在很多人垃圾不分类
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.93,0:00:44.53,ASS,,0,0,0,,害我们被骂
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.34,0:00:49.67,ASS,,0,0,0,,真是讨厌的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.41,0:00:54.40,ASS,,0,0,0,,就是他
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.75,0:01:00.28,ASS,,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.83,0:01:11.02,ASS,,0,0,0,,我看他没工作吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.30,0:01:13.42,ASS,,0,0,0,,没工作？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.63,0:01:16.83,ASS,,0,0,0,,这么早就回来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.17,0:01:19.36,ASS,,0,0,0,,打扮也随便
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.57,0:01:23.51,ASS,,0,0,0,,一定是打工或无业吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.71,0:01:25.97,ASS,,0,0,0,,真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.64,0:01:29.11,ASS,,0,0,0,,真恶心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.25,0:01:34.45,ASS,,0,0,0,,你一定要小心唷
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.39,0:01:38.91,ASS,,0,0,0,,那种怪人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.14,0:01:55.59,ASS,,0,0,0,,可以吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.68,0:02:03.87,ASS,,0,0,0,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.01,0:02:07.88,ASS,,0,0,0,,妈下个月18号生日
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.42,0:02:12.88,ASS,,0,0,0,,你有空吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.36,0:02:16.62,ASS,,0,0,0,,不知道耶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.16,0:02:21.62,ASS,,0,0,0,,说不定没空唷
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.37,0:02:26.89,ASS,,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.50,0:02:31.23,ASS,,0,0,0,,那我自己去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.51,0:02:34.57,ASS,,0,0,0,,抱歉啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.72,0:02:46.85,ASS,,0,0,0,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.19,0:02:50.45,ASS,,0,0,0,,加油唷\N怎啦？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.26,0:02:56.39,ASS,,0,0,0,,还要喝对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.23,0:03:27.16,ASS,,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.83,0:03:31.09,ASS,,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.43,0:03:34.70,ASS,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.18,0:03:48.44,ASS,,0,0,0,,那个...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.98,0:03:54.72,ASS,,0,0,0,,掉了\N抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.82,0:04:27.62,ASS,,0,0,0,,怎么啦？喝这么多
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.09,0:04:31.89,ASS,,0,0,0,,怎样 不行唷
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.29,0:04:34.95,ASS,,0,0,0,,不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.23,0:04:38.29,ASS,,0,0,0,,那是怎样！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.37,0:04:44.10,ASS,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.50,0:04:48.77,ASS,,0,0,0,,家里的事全交给你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.17,0:04:52.84,ASS,,0,0,0,,我只要工作就好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.71,0:04:58.84,ASS,,0,0,0,,可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.85,0:05:03.25,ASS,,0,0,0,,好 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.27,0:05:21.47,ASS,,0,0,0,,今天好热唷
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.47,0:05:23.46,ASS,,0,0,0,,对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.74,0:05:26.54,ASS,,0,0,0,,要小心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.81,0:05:30.01,ASS,,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.15,0:05:34.14,ASS,,0,0,0,,小心唷
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.55,0:05:39.01,ASS,,0,0,0,,怎么啦？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.02,0:05:42.29,ASS,,0,0,0,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.69,0:05:47.10,ASS,,0,0,0,,你最近没干吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.23,0:05:52.63,ASS,,0,0,0,,啥？\N做爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.37,0:05:58.57,ASS,,0,0,0,,说啥啊\N还装啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.18,0:06:03.11,ASS,,0,0,0,,这很重要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.65,0:06:07.98,ASS,,0,0,0,,不小心就会一直没做唷
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.25,0:06:11.45,ASS,,0,0,0,,我电视上有看到
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.85,0:06:14.32,ASS,,0,0,0,,皮肤也会变糟
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.59,0:06:17.65,ASS,,0,0,0,,所以我天天做
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.79,0:06:22.20,ASS,,0,0,0,,你也要注意唷
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.46,0:06:26.99,ASS,,0,0,0,,虽然很难开口
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.34,0:06:31.53,ASS,,0,0,0,,不过你没做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.81,0:06:38.47,ASS,,0,0,0,,这样不好唷
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.48,0:06:40.47,ASS,,0,0,0,,要做爱唷
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.48,0:06:42.47,ASS,,0,0,0,,对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.82,0:06:47.35,ASS,,0,0,0,,一周至少一次
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.69,0:06:51.68,ASS,,0,0,0,,太少啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.96,0:06:56.16,ASS,,0,0,0,,自己要积极
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.50,0:07:00.23,ASS,,0,0,0,,我也差不多
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.43,0:07:03.96,ASS,,0,0,0,,加油
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.97,0:07:05.96,ASS,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.11,0:07:09.51,ASS,,0,0,0,,我忘了东西
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.71,0:07:13.58,ASS,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.91,0:07:18.11,ASS,,0,0,0,,我们家也是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.12,0:07:20.11,ASS,,0,0,0,,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.39,0:07:24.45,ASS,,0,0,0,,没问题啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.59,0:07:28.46,ASS,,0,0,0,,可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.86,0:08:04.85,ASS,,0,0,0,,我要早起耶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.13,0:08:07.86,ASS,,0,0,0,,你搞啥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.40,0:08:12.80,ASS,,0,0,0,,那啥表情？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.21,0:08:18.34,ASS,,0,0,0,,我可是很累耶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.54,0:08:23.34,ASS,,0,0,0,,搞清楚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.37,0:08:50.70,ASS,,0,0,0,,那个...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.64,0:08:58.05,ASS,,0,0,0,,传阅版
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.58,0:09:02.92,ASS,,0,0,0,,没传给我耶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.32,0:09:05.91,ASS,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.79,0:09:11.59,ASS,,0,0,0,,那个...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.46,0:09:16.06,ASS,,0,0,0,,你很寂寞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.80,0:09:22.00,ASS,,0,0,0,,我看不下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.81,0:09:26.74,ASS,,0,0,0,,你寂寞的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.35,0:09:35.01,ASS,,0,0,0,,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.22,0:09:39.21,ASS,,0,0,0,,对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.42,0:09:45.76,ASS,,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.89,0:09:48.62,ASS,,0,0,0,,然后啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.03,0:09:52.90,ASS,,0,0,0,,你干什么 住手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.10,0:09:56.16,ASS,,0,0,0,,这是怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.30,0:10:00.71,ASS,,0,0,0,,我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.71,0:10:02.70,ASS,,0,0,0,,我一直看着
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.18,0:10:09.45,ASS,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.65,0:10:13.05,ASS,,0,0,0,,别乱动\N住手
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.13,0:10:31.20,ASS,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.47,0:10:35.74,ASS,,0,0,0,,我来满足你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.21,0:10:42.08,ASS,,0,0,0,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.35,0:10:46.15,ASS,,0,0,0,,别大叫
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.29,0:10:57.63,ASS,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.10,0:11:02.83,ASS,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.84,0:11:04.83,ASS,,0,0,0,,拜托你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.57,0:11:10.98,ASS,,0,0,0,,我来满足你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.98,0:11:12.97,ASS,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.31,0:11:17.72,ASS,,0,0,0,,乖乖听话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.12,0:11:26.18,ASS,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.79,0:11:31.99,ASS,,0,0,0,,没有满足对吧
