Dialogue: 0,0:50:01.50,0:50:04.56,ASS,,0,0,0,,老公？
Dialogue: 0,0:50:26.72,0:50:30.05,ASS,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:50:30.19,0:50:34.13,ASS,,0,0,0,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:50:34.39,0:50:39.26,ASS,,0,0,0,,你不是接受我了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:50:46.87,0:50:50.14,ASS,,0,0,0,,很困扰的
Dialogue: 0,0:50:50.41,0:50:54.68,ASS,,0,0,0,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:50:55.75,0:50:59.55,ASS,,0,0,0,,你说啥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:50:59.69,0:51:04.49,ASS,,0,0,0,,你明明接受我了
Dialogue: 0,0:51:05.96,0:51:10.29,ASS,,0,0,0,,已经忘不了我的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:51:10.96,0:51:13.96,ASS,,0,0,0,,我的肉棒
Dialogue: 0,0:51:14.97,0:51:18.03,ASS,,0,0,0,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:51:32.98,0:51:36.44,ASS,,0,0,0,,我懂的
Dialogue: 0,0:51:36.45,0:51:38.45,ASS,,0,0,0,,想要吧
Dialogue: 0,0:51:44.53,0:51:47.46,ASS,,0,0,0,,拜托...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:47.60,0:51:51.80,ASS,,0,0,0,,不要这么粗鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:51:52.74,0:51:56.54,ASS,,0,0,0,,不要粗鲁啊
